e the sub-command name.\nThis name is used to identify the sub-command in usage and command line.\nE.g. \"my_app <name>\" will exectute the <name> command.","parameters":[{"name":"Cmd","description":""}]}},{"id":"49f04cc6c4d0fba4","name":"Name","qualified_name":"CLIC.Subcommand.Name","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"../../../home/runner/.local/share/alire/builds/clic_0.3.0_56bbdc00/999105376a33c1da6df82bf23715d18a8c81ec1b7c97d521e34e338ee687fd74/src/clic-subcommand.ads","line":146,"column":13},"code":"function Name (This : Help_Topic) return Identifier","documentation":{"description":"This name is used to identify the topic in usage and command line.\nE.g. \"my_app help <name>\" will display the content of the <name> topic.","parameters":[{"name":"This","description":""}]}},{"id":"1cbad449f4fbc564","name":"No_TTY","qualified_name":"CLIC.Subcommand.No_TTY","kind":"ada_function","location":{"file":"../../../home/runner/.local/share/alire/builds/clic_0.3.0_56bbdc00/999105376a33c1da6df82bf23715d18a8c81ec1b7c97d521e34e338ee687fd74/src/clic-subcommand.ads","line":165,"column":13},"code":"function No_TTY (Str : String) return String","documentation":{"description":"Use this function for the TTY_* generic parameters of\nCLIC.Subcommand.Instance if you don't want or need TTY formating.","parameters":[{"name":"Str","description":""}]}},{"id":"255601d729deb406","name":"Setup_Switches","qualified_name":"CLIC.Subcommand.Setup_Switches","kind":"ada_procedure","location":{"file":"../../../home/runner/.local/share/alire/builds/clic_0.3.0_56bbdc00/999105376a33c1da6df82bf23715d18a8c81ec1b7c97d521e34e338ee687fd74/src/clic-subcommand.ads","line":117,"column":14},"code":"procedure Setup_Switches\n  (Cmd    : in out Command;\n   Config : in out Switches_Configuration)","documentation":{"description":"Gets called once the command has been identified, but before the call to\nExecute. Config must be set up with the switches used by the command.","parameters":[{"name":"Cmd","descrip